# Card

**Figma:** [Card](https://www.figma.com/design/AW4jk9SLPKlSqYt6NZ1QK5/Qure-%3C%3E-Figma-Design-system?node-id=2143-13485&p=f&m=dev)

Structure, variants, content blocks, and token mappings below are derived from Figma node 2143:13485.

---

## Variables (from design-system-tokens.mdc)

| Use | Token |
|-----|-------|
| Default surface | `--bg-base-default` |
| Featured/primary surface | `--bg-brand-default` |
| Selected surface | `--bg-brand-tertiary` |
| Selected border | `--border-brand-default` |
| Image placeholder | `--bg-base-tertiary` |
| Title | `--text-base-default` |
| Body text | `--text-base-secondary` |
| Primary button | `--bg-brand-default` |
| Secondary button | `--border-base-default`, `--text-base-default` |
| Text on brand | `--text-brand-on-brand` |

---

## Structure

- **Rule:** Fixed width in component set; auto layout and width defined by parent.
- **Padding:** Space/200–400.
- **Layout:** Vertical stack; optional image/icon → title → body → button.

---

## Structural variants (from Figma)

| Variant | Structure |
|---------|-----------|
| SIZE | [Icon?] → Title → Body text → Button |
| IMAGE | Image placeholder (top) → Title → Body text → Button |
| ICON | Leading icon → Title → Body text → Button |
| DEFAULT | Image placeholder → Title → Body text → Button |

---

## Content blocks

| Block | Token | Notes |
|-------|-------|-------|
| Title | `--text-base-default` | Bold; single or multi-line |
| Body text | `--text-base-secondary` | Multi-line |
| Button | Primary `--bg-brand-default` or secondary `--border-base-default` | Per variant |
| Image placeholder | `--bg-base-tertiary` | Aspect ratio per placement |

---

## Styled variants

| Variant | Surface | Text | Button |
|---------|---------|------|--------|
| Light card | `--bg-base-default` | `--text-base-default` | `--bg-brand-default` |
| Teal card | `--bg-brand-default` | `--text-brand-on-brand` | Secondary (grey) |
| Pricing card | `--bg-base-default` | `--text-base-default` | Prominent price; CTA at bottom |

---

## Specialized cards (from Figma)

- **Review card:** Star rating; Review title; Review body; Avatar + Reviewed name + Date.
- **Timer/Activity card:** Clock icon; time (e.g. 1:00); Body text.
- **Quote card:** Quote icon; quote text; Avatar + Name + Description.

---

## States

| State | Surface | Border |
|-------|---------|--------|
| Default | `--bg-base-default` or `--bg-brand-default` | `--border-base-default` |
| Selected | `--bg-brand-tertiary` | `--border-brand-default` |

---

## Implementation guidelines

- Use tokens from `design-system-tokens.mdc` only.
- Spacing: Space/200–400 internal; Space/400–600 between cards in grid.
- Do not invent variants; implement only what exists in Figma node 2143:13485.
